---
const codeLines = [
	'<span class="text-slate-500">&lt;</span><span class="text-fuchsia-400">main</span> <span class="text-emerald-400">class</span>=<span class="text-amber-300">"perfil"</span><span class="text-slate-500">&gt;</span>',
	'  <span class="text-slate-500">&lt;</span><span class="text-fuchsia-400">h1</span><span class="text-slate-500">&gt;</span>{{ nombre }}<span class="text-slate-500">&lt;/</span><span class="text-fuchsia-400">h1</span><span class="text-slate-500">&gt;</span>',
	'  <span class="text-slate-500">&lt;</span><span class="text-fuchsia-400">p</span><span class="text-slate-500">&gt;</span>Construyo productos para la web<span class="text-slate-500">&lt;/</span><span class="text-fuchsia-400">p</span><span class="text-slate-500">&gt;</span>',
	'  {{ proyectos_destacados }}',
	'  {{ actividad_github }}',
	'<span class="text-slate-500">&lt;/</span><span class="text-fuchsia-400">main</span><span class="text-slate-500">&gt;</span>',
];
---
<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
	<div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[.85fr_1.15fr]">
		<div data-reveal>
			<p class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[.2em] text-cyan-300">Tu espacio en la web</p>
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl">Empieza con tus datos. Termina con algo que se sienta tuyo.</h2>
			<p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-slate-400">Nosotros conectamos las piezas que cambian: repositorios, lenguajes y actividad. Tú decides cómo contarlas, qué destacar y qué dejar fuera.</p>
			<ul class="mt-7 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-300"><li>HTML y CSS editables</li><li>Vista previa mientras escribes</li><li>Datos de GitHub que se mantienen al día</li></ul>
		</div>
		<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#0d0d16] shadow-2xl" data-reveal>
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-white/10 px-4 py-3"><span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-400"></span><span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-amber-300"></span><span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-300"></span><span class="ml-auto text-xs text-slate-500">perfil.html</span></div>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2">
				<pre class="overflow-x-auto p-5 text-[12px] leading-7"><code>{codeLines.map((line) => <Fragment><span class="block" set:html={line} />{"\n"}</Fragment>)}</code></pre>
				<div class="m-3 rounded-xl bg-[#e7eee8] p-6 text-[#17211b]">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-3"><div class="grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full bg-[#17211b] text-xs font-bold text-emerald-300">CR</div><div><strong class="block">Camila Rojas</strong><span class="text-xs opacity-60">Santiago, Chile</span></div></div>
					<p class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold leading-tight">Construyo productos para la web.</p>
					<div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-[10px]"><span class="rounded border border-black/10 p-2">42 repositorios</span><span class="rounded border border-black/10 p-2">TypeScript</span></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
